      Guidance
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Changes to notifying an option to tax land and buildings during coronavirus (COVID-19)
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-third">
      <nav role="navigation" class="gem-c-translation-nav gem-c-translation-nav " aria-label="Translations">
    <ul class="gem-c-translation-nav__list">
        <li class="gem-c-translation-nav__list-item">
            <span lang="en">English</span>
        </li>
        <li class="gem-c-translation-nav__list-item">
            <a hreflang="cy" lang="cy" rel="alternate" class="gem-c-translation-nav__link " href="/guidance/changes-to-notifying-an-option-to-tax-land-and-buildings-during-coronavirus-covid-19.cy">Cymraeg</a>
        </li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  </div>

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Check temporary changes to the time limit and rules for notifying an option to tax land and buildings.</p>

  </div>
</div>

